OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early hill fog will soon
OL,6,Fclear. A dry day with long sunny
OL,7,Fspells and an increasingly brisk
OL,8,Feasterly breeze, especially over
OL,9,Fhills. Warm inland but cooler along
OL,10,Fcoasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening with some late
OL,13,Fsunny spells, though rather breezy. A
OL,14,Fclear night will follow, becoming
OL,15,Fchilly with a risk of rural frosts.
OL,16,FWinds falling light away from hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,165,160,301,260,100,100
