OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother day of long sunny
OL,6,Fspells, though windy once again, these
OL,7,Fstrongest near coasts. Warm, though
OL,8,Ffeeling cooler in exposed areas and
OL,9,Falong eastern coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday,
OL,12,Fpatchy cloud and sunny intervals, very
OL,13,Fwarm, chance of showers. Cloudy
OL,14,FSaturday and Sunday, risk of rain or
OL,15,Fshowers at times. Cooler with
OL,16,Fgenerally light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
